      "root_cause": "renderGraph() unconditionally reads ai.implant and ai.bridge at line 138-139. calcAIMulti() returns implant2/bridge4/cantilever — no .implant or .bridge — so both are undefined, and undefined - number = NaN, Math.max(65, NaN) = NaN (JS spec), propagating NaN into all SVG attributes. Wave 4 modularization introduced renderMainPanels() which routes ALL ai modes through renderGraph(), exposing the gap that renderCost() already guards with early returns but renderGraph() did not.",
